# Title: Okta Policy Rule Modified or Deleted
# Author: Austin Songer @austinsonger
# Date: 2021-09-12
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects when an Policy Rule is Modified or Deleted.
# MITRE Tactic: Impact
# Tags: attack.impact
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/identity/okta/okta_policy_rule_modified_or_deleted.yml

eventType IN ("policy.rule.update", "policy.rule.delete")